
This directory contains the following informational files:

INSTALL_NOTES:

    This file contains instructions for building or installing MeshTV.
    It contains instructions for installing a pre-built distribution or
    building MeshTV on common Unix systems.  This is the file you should
    start with, and is usually the only file you will need to read.

CONFIGURE_NOTES

    This file contains an overview of configure and describes useful
    information for developers.  It may also contain useful information
    if you have problems building MeshTV.
    
BUILD_NOTES

    This file contains an overview of the build process and describes
    useful information for developers.  It may also contain useful
    information if you have problems building MeshTV.

INSTALL_FAQ

    A MeshTV installation FAQ.
